# Demo frontend env template — demo.app-juli.com (apps/demo)
#
# Copy to ~/Juli-AI-v2/apps/demo/.env.production on the VPS if needed.
# NEVER commit real values. Mock mode requires no backend credentials or API URL.
#
# The Demo app ships with hardcoded mock data — no NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL,
# DATABASE_URL, Supabase, or TikTok secrets are required at build or runtime.

# Optional public app URL (informational; not required for mock mode).
# NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=https://demo.app-juli.com
